    in_love: 'Amaterasu in love is the *cosmic-feminine-solar* — the partner whose light is the warmth-and-fertility of the household-as-cosmos, whose withdrawal into the rock-cave is the most-frightening event in any relationship (and whose coaxing-back-out requires the *eight-million kami in assembly* — that is, the whole community gathering at the river-bed with their full ingenuity, not just the one anxious-partner trying alone). The Amaterasu-partner is the one whose *light is so central* that her depression *darkens the entire cosmos*, and whose return requires not argument but *ecstatic celebration* (Ame-no-Uzume\'s laughing dance) and *curious mirror* (the partner who is willing to be *coaxed by what is reflective* rather than *demanded by what is direct*). The shadow is the partner who has been *expected to provide cosmic-light without limit* — the *imperial-ancestral burden* of being the *source-of-warmth for everyone* with no rock-cave allowed, no withdrawal permitted, no Niinamesai recognized. The other shadow: the relationship that has tried to *demand-the-mirror-be-shown* (the partner who, like a tourist at Ise, has wanted to *see* the *Yata-no-Kagami* directly when the entire structure of the relationship has been *the mirror-is-honored-by-being-veiled*).',
