      'Whose Uzume-foundational-performing-arts-priestess have I flattened into team-morale-event-planning — what figure in my work or family has the *cosmic-mirth-and-erotic-comic-cosmic-priestess* function that I have been *failing to recognize as the foundational lineage of the entire performing-art-of-the-organization*?'
